<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821648>
    dc:description "FIGURES 469–473. Kalopolynema ema (Schauff & Grissell). 469, head, anterior; 470, head, posterior; 471a, head, lateral; 471b, head lateral (internal) showing ocular apodeme; 472, head, dorsal; 473, antenna. Scale bars=50 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821648/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821656>
    dc:description "FIGURES 480–485. Kalopolynema ema (Schauff & Grissell), head. 480, anterior; 481, posterior; 482, lateral; 483, dorsal; 484, ventral; 485, mouthparts. Scale bars=50 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821656/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821644>
    dc:description "FIGURE 467. Kalopolynema ema (Schauff & Grissell), habitus. USA, Ohio, Summit Co., Singer Lake, 339m, 40°59'N 81°29'W, 7–8.viii.2006, H. Clebsch, T. Pucci, kettle lake/bog + forest edge. Scale bar=500 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821644/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821652>
    dc:description "FIGURES 476, 477. Kalopolynema ema (Schauff & Grissell). 476, wings; 477, metasoma, composite (dorsal + ventral). Scale bars=200 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821652/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821658>
    dc:description "FIGURES 486–493. Kalopolynema ema (Schauff & Grissell), mesosoma. 486, dorsal; 487, lateral; 488, ventral; 489, anterior; 490, posterior; 491, petiole, dorsal; 482, petiole, ventral; 483, petiole, lateral. Scale bars: 486–490=100 μm; 491, 492=20 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821658/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821646>
    dc:description "FIGURE 468. Kalopolynema mizelli Triapitsyn & Berezovskiy, holotype, habitus + labels. Scale bar=1000 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821646/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821660>
    dc:description "FIGURES 494–499. Kalopolynema ema (Schauff & Grissell), mesosoma. 494, dorsal; 495, ventral; 496, lateral; 497, anterior; 498, apex of gaster, dorsal; 499, apex of gaster, lateral. Scale bars: 494–497=200 μm; 498, 499=20 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821660/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

